caption:
Back in 2019/20, Wrexham finished 18th in the National League, narrowly avoiding relegation by just 3 points. 👀

In February 2021, Rob McElhenney and Ryan Reynolds completed their takeover of the club for $2.5 million. 💰 

Since then, Wrexham have gained three promotions and will play in the Championship next season 📈

⬆️ 2023: Promoted to League Two
⬆️ 2024: Promoted to League One
⬆️ 2025: Promoted to the Championship

An incredible turnaround 👏
